### Dataset Information

**Dataset Name:** Accident Detection from CCTV Footage

**Dataset Source:** Kaggle

**Dataset Link:** https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ckay16/accident-detection-from-cctv-footage

**Field:** Transportation and Traffic Intelligence

**Description:**
This dataset contains CCTV traffic surveillance images categorized into two classes: Accident and Non Accident. The images are collected from traffic monitoring footage and are intended for developing deep learning models that can automatically detect road accidents from visual data.

**Classes:**

1. Accident
2. Non Accident

**Image Type:**
Traffic surveillance/CCTV images

**Dataset Structure:**

* Train Set
* Validation Set
* Test Set

**Number of Classes:** 2 (Binary Classification)

